@startuml
title WordPress Sequence

participant Application
participant WordPressClient
participant WordPress

Application -> WordPressClient: upload_media(images)
WordPressClient -> WordPress: POST /wp-json/wp/v2/media
WordPress --> WordPressClient: media ids
Application -> WordPressClient: get_or_create_category()
WordPressClient -> WordPress: GET/POST categories
Application -> WordPressClient: create_post()
WordPressClient -> WordPress: POST /wp-json/wp/v2/posts
WordPress --> WordPressClient: post id / url

@enduml
